    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Lissodendoryx (Anomodoryx) vulcanus Cavalcanti, Santos & Pinheiro, 2014. A, preserved specimen (UFPEPOR 3249); B, thick section showing the choanosome and ectosome; C, size variation of tylotes; D, raphides; E, arcuate isochelae; F, sigmas. Scales: A = 2 cm; B = 800 µm; C–D = 25 µm; E–F = 12.5 µm." ;
